&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nurse Practitioner - Wound Care&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As an experienced or new-to-wound-care Nurse Practitioner, you&#39;ll manage your patient outcomes based on your clinical expertise and direction. At Skilled Wound Care, you are a valued member of a close-knit team, making a real difference in the lives of patients with chronic wounds.&lt;br&gt;We&#39;re a leading national wound care physician group seeking motivated and driven Nurse Practitioners of all backgrounds to join our team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MEANINGFUL WORK&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Provide comprehensive wound care to patients in nursing facilities, utilizing the latest advancements in wound healing - including debridement and advanced dressings. You&#39;ll work within a collaborative, physician-led team model that supports your clinical growth and patient outcomes every step of the way.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;COMPREHENSIVE NP WOUND CARE TRAINING&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
