&lt;p&gt;We are a nation-wide mobile surgical practice, focused on skin, wound, and ostomy patient issues in nursing home settings. Since 2007, Skilled Wound Care has been innovating mobile medicine delivery in the nursing facility. Therefore, if you are seeking a new and exciting specialty in a hands-on bedside procedure-oriented practice, you should reply right now. This would set you up to become an expert in your field and highly advanced in your subspecialty. We provide mentoring, professional guidance, covered advanced wound care and surgical training and on-boarding.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To learn more information contact us today at (310) 445-5999!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Or visit us at www.skilledwoundcare.com&lt;/p&gt;
