&lt;p&gt;We are looking for diligent physician warriors who love doing procedures and who value the importance of work/life balance. Work hard, play hard, that&#39;s the motto. And because of that, our job satisfaction rating is well over 90%! Just check out these benefits!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Benefits for all candidates:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Choose Your Own Schedule&lt;br&gt;2-5 Day Work-Week&lt;br&gt;Free Weekends&lt;br&gt;Protected Time-Off&lt;br&gt;No Calls&lt;br&gt;Full malpractice insurance&lt;br&gt;Equipment&lt;br&gt;2 Fully covered weekend educational retreats per year with 16 hours of CME each&lt;br&gt;Work in Your Community&lt;br&gt;Yearly and quarterly bonus potential based on performance&lt;br&gt;Independent Contractor, Fee for Service Pay Model&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE POSITION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re able to offer you all of these amazing benefits by transitioning you from hospitals and clinics over to long-term care facilities. Our practice specializes in consistently delivering exceptional wound care and unparalleled bedside procedures to patients in nursing homes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are on the frontier of wound care science and innovation. This is your opportunity to learn from the best in the field, be trained in advanced bedside procedures &amp;amp; wound care, to be at the cutting edge of this science, and to bring advanced procedures to patients&#39; bedsides.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;LOCATION&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our home office is located in Los Angeles, California, but the beauty of this job is you can work from anywhere. We have relationships with facilities all across the nation and are adding new locations every day. You can choose the facilities that work best for you.&lt;/p&gt;
